# 🧪 QA Dev Playground

This is my dedicated automation testing sandbox, powered by:

- ✅ [Cypress](https://www.cypress.io/)
- 🎭 [Playwright](https://playwright.dev/)
- 🌐 Node.js (managed via [Volta](https://volta.sh))

---

## 🔧 Setup

```bash
cd ~/qa-dev
npm install
````

---

## 🚀 Scripts

| Command               | Description                |
| --------------------- | -------------------------- |
| `npx cypress open`    | Launch Cypress test runner |
| `npx playwright test` | Run Playwright tests (CLI) |

---

## 🗂️ Structure

```txt
qa-dev/
├── cypress/              # Cypress tests & configs
│   ├── e2e/
│   └── support/
├── tests/                # Playwright test files
├── node_modules/
├── package.json
├── .gitignore
```

---

## 💫 Notes

* All tools are installed via [Volta](https://volta.sh) for locked-in versions
* This repo is used for learning, tinkering, and sharpening my QA engineering craft

